        "acne_shield_HaxkhL": {
          "type": "acne-shield",
          "settings": {
            "tag": "01 — Clinical-Grade Germ Protection",
            "heading": "THE ANTI-ACNE SHIELD",
            "description": "<p>Most sleep acne is caused by bacteria that accumulate on your pillowcase and transfer back to your skin while you sleep. The <strong>Silver Grid</strong> woven into the Jax Sheets continuously inhibits the growth of those bacteria on the fabric surface, meaning your face rests on a significantly cleaner environment every night.<br/>For skin prone to breakouts, conventional pillowcases offer no protection against bacterial buildup between washes. The Jax Sheets work against it constantly.</p>",
            "card_title": "MICROBIOME PROTECTION",
            "stat_value": "99.9%",
            "stat_unit": "Kill Rate",
            "stat_title": "Bacteria Neutralization",
            "stat_desc": "Destroys acne-causing microbes every 180 seconds.",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "style_preset": "default",
            "html_id": "",
            "enable_section_animation": false,
            "tooltip_trigger": "Silver Grid",
            "tooltip_content": "<p><strong>What is it?</strong></p><p>A silver grid is a network of ultra-fine silver threads woven directly into the fabric at precise intervals, forming a continuous grid structure throughout the textile. Unlike silver ion treatments that are applied to the surface of a fabric and degrade with washing, a woven silver grid is a permanent part of the sheet's construction.</p><p><strong>How does it fight acne?</strong></p><p>The silver ions continuously neutralize the bacteria that cause breakouts — Propionibacterium acnes and Staphylococcus aureus — directly on the fabric surface. Your skin rests on a cleaner environment every night without any additional effort.</p>",
