            "heading": "FRICTION-FREE HAIR CARE",
            "description": "<p>Standard cotton and polyester fabrics have microscopic irregularities that catch on hair cuticles as you move through the night, causing frizz, micro-tears, and breakage over time. The Jax Sheets are engineered at a fiber level to be exceptionally smooth, significantly reducing that physical drag against your hair. Your cuticles are less likely to snag or break during sleep, helping to maintain smoother, healthier hair over time, without the heat trapping qualities that make traditional silk uncomfortable for most sleepers.</p>",
