            "tag": "03 — A Breathable Surface for Clearer Skin",
            "heading": "OIL & HUMIDITY MANAGEMENT",
            "description": "<p>Skin inflammation often occurs when sweat and excess sebum (oil) are trapped against the skin in a damp environment. To manage this, we've woven in <strong>Volcanic Ash</strong> and <strong>Coconut Charcoal</strong>. The ash acts as a natural desiccant, pulling humidity away from your skin before it becomes liquid sweat, while the charcoal helps absorb excess oils. By keeping the sleep surface dry and oil-neutral, the fabric prevents the \"clammy\" environment that leads to congested pores and morning puffiness.</p>",
