          "type": "hc-extended-lifespan",
          "settings": {
            "tag": "01 — Extended Lifespan",
            "heading": "LESS WASHING = LONGER LIFESPAN",
            "description": "<p>Most bedding wears out prematurely due to the stress of frequent laundering. High heat and friction break down fibers, but bacteria and odors are what force those cycles. Jax Sheets solve this at the source. Our integrated technology stays fresh for much longer, significantly reducing the need for washing. By minimizing fabric stress, Jax Sheets preserve their original smoothness and performance for years, not months.</p>",
