            "description": "<p>Traditional bedding is a hidden recurring expense. Standard sheets require constant spending on water, electricity, and high-heat drying to manage bacteria and odors. Worse, this frequent laundering is what ultimately destroys the fabric, forcing you into a cycle of expensive replacements every year or two.</p><p>Jax Sheets turn your bedding into a long-term asset. By staying fresh for weeks, they significantly reduce laundry overhead and extend the lifespan of your sheets by years. Bedding that manages its own hygiene literally costs less to own—saving you time, money, and the hassle of constant maintenance.</p>",
